===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|xno|en}} {{m|fro|alai}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|aloi}}, from {{m|fro|aloiier}}.

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# A [[metal]] that is a combination of two or more [[element]]s, at least one of which is a metal.
# An [[admixture]]; something added which [[stain]]s, [[taint]]s etc.
#* {{RQ:Flr Mntgn Essays}}, II.20:
#*: ''Metrodorus'' said that in sadnesse there is some '''aloy''' of pleasure.

